'''夏军'''（{{bd|1963年||}}）是一位中国建筑师，<ref name=bio>{{cite web |url=http://www.ctbuh.org/CongressCommittees/LocalSteering/JunXia/tabid/3013/language/en-US/Default.aspx |title=Jun Xia |website=[[Council_on_Tall_Buildings_and_Urban_Habitat|Council on Tall Buildings and Urban Habitat]] |accessdate=2018-12-30 |archive-date=2019-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190114171921/http://www.ctbuh.org/CongressCommittees/LocalSteering/JunXia/tabid/3013/language/en-US/Default.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Atlantic>{{cite journal | journal=[[The_Atlantic|The Atlantic]] | url=https://www.theatlantic.com/magazine/archive/2012/11/jun-xia/309130/ | title=Brave Thinkers 2012: Jun Xia | date=November 2012 | accessdate=2018-12-30 | archive-date=2020-10-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030054347/https://www.theatlantic.com/magazine/archive/2012/11/jun-xia/309130/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>美国Gensler建筑事务所中国区负责人，董事会成员。<ref name=Bloomberg>{{cite web|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/research/stocks/private/person.asp?personId=317809821&privcapId=4259493&previousCapId=4259493&previousTitle=M.%20Arthur%20Gensler%20Jr.%20&%20Associates,%20Inc. | title= Jun Xia Executive Profile & Biography | website=[[Bloomberg_L.P.|Bloomberg L.P.]] | author=[[S&P_Global_Market_Intelligence|S&P Global Market Intelligence]] | accessdate=2019-01-01}}</ref>

==生平==
1963出生于[[上海|上海]]，1984年毕业于[[同济大学|同济大学]]建筑系城市规划专业，后任职于[[北京|北京]][[中国城市规划设计研究院|中国城市规划设计研究院]]，1987年赴美留学，后毕业于[[科罗拉多大学丹佛分校|科罗拉多大学丹佛分校]]。1991年加入美国Gensler建筑事务所。2003年Gensler在[[北京|北京]]和[[上海|上海]]分布设立办事处，由此返回中国担任负责人。2008年Gensler的“龙型”设计方案竞标[[上海中心大厦|上海中心大厦]]胜出，成为项目主要负责人。<ref name=Forbes>{{cite journal|date=August 7, 2013|author=Russell Flannery|work=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|title='There Is Never Going To Be A Building Like This In The U.S.'|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/russellflannery/2013/08/07/there-is-never-going-to-be-a-building-like-this-in-the-u-s/|accessdate=2018-10-09|archive-date=2021-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204011545/https://www.forbes.com/sites/russellflannery/2013/08/07/there-is-never-going-to-be-a-building-like-this-in-the-u-s/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|date=June 6, 2013|work=[[Metropolis_(architecture_magazine)|Metropolis]]|author=Ben Ikenson|title=What's Inside Gensler’s Secret Sauce?|url=https://www.metropolismag.com/architecture/genslers-secret-sauce/|accessdate=2018-10-09|archive-date=2016-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160523034145/http://www.metropolismag.com/June-2013/Genslers-Secret-Sauce/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|date=June 25, 2015|work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|author=Julie Makinen|title=U.S. design firm puts its stamp on Shanghai skyline|url=https://www.latimes.com/business/la-fi-shanghai-tower-20150625-story.html|accessdate=2018-12-29|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108124202/https://www.latimes.com/business/la-fi-shanghai-tower-20150625-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |title=夏军 中国第一高楼的背后 |date=April 21, 2015 |work=安邸中国新节奏 |url=https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/8NCDzzGQKFCRSq-Yy3ZH8w |journal= |access-date=2021-01-30 |archive-date=2021-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210203205547/https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/8NCDzzGQKFCRSq-Yy3ZH8w |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |title=夏军 不求最高，只求最好 |date=Jan 26, 2015 |wo